---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Kontakt">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>Kontakt</h1>
    <p>
      Sme vám k dispozícii. Napíšte nám alebo zavolajte a radi vám poradíme.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="grid">
    <div class="card info">
      <h2>Kontaktné údaje</h2>
      <ul class="details">
        <li>
          <strong>E‑mail:</strong>
          <a href="mailto:info@example.com">info@example.com</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Telefón:</strong>
          <a href="tel:+421000000000">+421 000 000 000</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Adresa:</strong>
          —
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Otvorené:</strong>
          Po–Pi 9:00–17:00
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="note">
        <p>
          Pre rýchlejšie spracovanie prosím uveďte predmet a krátky popis vašej požiadavky.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card form">
      <h2>Napíšte nám</h2>
      <form method="post" action="#">
        <div class="field">
          <label for="name">Meno</label>
          <input id="name" name="name" type="text" required autocomplete="name" />
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="email">E‑mail</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required autocomplete="email" />
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="subject">Predmet</label>
          <input id="subject" name="subject" type="text" />
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="message">Správa</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
          <button type="submit">Odoslať</button>
        </div>
      </form>

      <p class="hint">
        Odoslaním súhlasíte so spracovaním uvedených údajov výhradne za účelom vybavenia vašej požiadavky.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  section {
    margin: 1.25rem 0;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .card {
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .info .details {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .info .note {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .form form {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .field {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  label {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  input[type="text"],
  input[type="email"],
  textarea {
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.7rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    background: #fff;
    color: #111827;
  }

  input:focus,
  textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: #93c5fd;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15, 98, 254, 0.15);
  }

  .actions {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  button[type="submit"] {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #0f62fe;
    color: #ffffff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  button[type="submit"]:hover {
    background: #0b53d6;
  }

  a {
    color: #0f62fe;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
